data.description: Immediate Move-In! New Colina Wedgewood Forest Home. 2715 SF plan. Location, location, location--lakefront and woods. 3-car garage, 4/bed/2.5 bath/ study/game-room, fully sodded 13,242 SF Homesite. All-natural gas energy efficient home will save you $. Four sides brick and stone front accents. The interior selections are bright and airy to include 42" white upgrade cabinets, huge kitchen/breakfast bar. Extensive 6 x 24" ceramic tile throughout the entry, living room and wet areas, stainless steel appliances to include our premium 5 burner range & 9" farm sink, 2" blinds, Garden tub, sep. shower, Tankless H20, garage door openers, Smart Home Electronics pkg, Pex Plumbing, Lennox 16 Seer-A/C. Taexx Pest Control. Don't miss out. It's only 5 minutes from Lake Conroe, EZ access to Willis, Huntsville, Spring, Magnolia, Energy Corridor, The Woodlands Mall, Work and Shop in the City and Come Home to Wedgewood Forest.
